        "The Principle of Auto-Suggestion: You can program your subconscious mind through repetition. Read your goals out loud twice a day, visualizing and feeling the emotion of having already achieved them.",
        "Specialized Knowledge Over General Knowledge: Having a lot of general knowledge doesn't make you rich. Wealth requires highly specialized knowledge, smartly organized and directed toward a specific, practical goal.",
