                "The Twilight State: The best time to reprogram your subconscious is just before going to sleep and right after waking up. In a drowsy, relaxed state, negative conscious thoughts are minimized.",
                "Imagination Overcomes Willpower: When your desires and imagination are in conflict, your imagination always wins. You cannot force success with willpower; you must mentally visualize and feel the success.",
