                "The Power of Leverage: To scale your impact, you need leverage. Labor and capital require permission. Code and media (software, books, podcasts) are permissionless leverage. They work for you 24/7.",
                "Compound Interest in Everything: All the major returns in life—wealth, relationships, and knowledge—come from compound interest. Play long-term games with long-term, trustworthy people.",
                "Accountability: Embrace accountability and take business risks under your own name. Society will reward you with responsibility, equity, and leverage when you own your failures as publicly as your successes.",
